Better Homes And Gardens Real Estate Bloomtree Realty

data.description: Come see this beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath home set in the highly desirable Sandretto Hills neighborhood. Home features a large living room and upgraded kitchen with granite counters and new appliances. The split floor plan offers plenty of privacy on either. The backyard is a gardeners dream, with raised garden beds, multiple fruit tree's and a gardening shed. Backyard also features a large rv gate and rv parking pad. With No Hoa and close to Embry Riddle and downtown this home is very convenient. Recent upgrades include a  new roof and synthetic 40yr stucco.
